      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and it is in stunning shape! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. I\u2019m happy to answer any questions or show you around the car\u2014shoot me a message!",
