    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-quality masterpiece that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since its first mile. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like factory finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Step inside to an interior that still retains its original new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery is taut and supple, free of any creasing or bolster wear, while the hand-polished wood trim remains vibrant and scratch-free. Every electronic component, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium surround-sound system, functions with surgical precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships\u2014all records are organized and included. This sale comes complete with both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, and a set of unused plush floor mats. This is a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands perfection without compromise.",
